## Reverse Array

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int[] arr = {1,2,3,4,5};

        int left = 0;
        int right = arr.length-1;

        while(left < right)
        {
            int temp = arr[left];
            arr[left] = arr[right];
            arr[right] = temp;

            left++;
            right--;
        }

        for(int x : arr)
            System.out.print(x+" ");
    }
}
```

Output

```text
5 4 3 2 1
```

TC: O(n)

SC: O(1)

