## Reverse String

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        String s = "hello";

        String rev = "";

        for(int i=s.length()-1;i>=0;i--)
        {
            rev += s.charAt(i);
        }

        System.out.println(rev);
    }
}
```

Output

```text
olleh
```

TC: O(n)

---

## Palindrome String

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        String s = "madam";

        int i=0;
        int j=s.length()-1;

        boolean flag=true;

        while(i<j)
        {
            if(s.charAt(i)!=s.charAt(j))
            {
                flag=false;
                break;
            }

            i++;
            j--;
        }

        System.out.println(flag);
    }
}
```

Output

```text
true
```

