# 5. Recursion

### Definition

Function calling itself.

---

## Factorial

```java
static int factorial(int n)
{
    if(n==0)
        return 1;

    return n*factorial(n-1);
}
```

Output

```text
factorial(5)=120
```

TC: O(n)

SC: O(n)

---

## Fibonacci

```java
static int fib(int n)
{
    if(n<=1)
        return n;

    return fib(n-1)+fib(n-2);
}
```

Output

```text
fib(6)=8
```

TC: O(2ⁿ)

SC: O(n)

