## Subsets

```java
import java.util.*;

public class Main {

    static void subset(int[] arr,
                       int index,
                       List<Integer> curr)
    {
        if(index==arr.length)
        {
            System.out.println(curr);
            return;
        }

        curr.add(arr[index]);

        subset(arr,index+1,curr);

        curr.remove(curr.size()-1);

        subset(arr,index+1,curr);
    }

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        int[] arr={1,2};

        subset(arr,0,new ArrayList<>());
    }
}
```

Output

```text
[1, 2]
[1]
[2]
[]
```

TC: O(2ⁿ)

