# 6. Searching

## Linear Search

```java
int target = 30;

for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++)
{
    if(arr[i]==target)
    {
        System.out.println(i);
        break;
    }
}
```

TC: O(n)

---

## Binary Search

```java
int low=0;
int high=arr.length-1;

while(low<=high)
{
    int mid=(low+high)/2;

    if(arr[mid]==target)
    {
        System.out.println(mid);
        break;
    }
    else if(arr[mid]<target)
        low=mid+1;
    else
        high=mid-1;
}
```

TC: O(log n)

